<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>코사모</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/output.css?v=<%= Date.now() %>">
</head>
<body class="min-h-dvh bg-gray-50 text-gray-800">
  <%- include('nav.ejs') %>

  <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 space-y-pr-28">

    <!-- 1️⃣ 첫 번째 박스 -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-pr-16 border border-gray-200 shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] p-pr-24">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">코사모에 오신 걸 환영합니다 👋</h1>
      <p class="mt-pr-8 text-gray-600 text-16m">
        조건에 맞는 팀원과 스터디를 찾아보세요.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-pr-24 flex justify-start">
        <a href="/list" 
           class="px-pr-24 py-pr-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-pr-10 text-16sb hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
          사람들 보기
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="flex justify-end">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-pr-16 border border-gray-200 shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] p-pr-24 w-full tamo:w-3/5 text-right">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">새로운 사람 찾기</h2>
        <p class="mt-pr-6 text-gray-600 text-16m">
          관심 분야, 기술스택으로 필터링해서 팀원을 찾아요.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-pr-24 flex justify-end">
          <a href="/people"
            class="px-pr-24 py-pr-12 bg-white text-blue-600 rounded-pr-10 text-16sb border border-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-50 transition inline-flex items-center gap-pr-6">
            가입한 사람들 보기
            <span class="text-sm">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- 3️⃣ 세 번째 박스 -->
    <section>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-pr-16 border border-gray-200 shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] p-pr-24 w-full tamo:w-3/5">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">실시간 대화</h2>
        <p class="mt-pr-6 text-gray-600 text-16m">
          채팅방 리스트에서 바로 이어서 대화할 수 있어요.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-pr-24 flex justify-start">
          <a href="/chat/list"
             class="px-pr-24 py-pr-12 bg-gray-800 text-white rounded-pr-10 text-16sb hover:bg-gray-900 transition">
            대화방 들어가기
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</body>
</html>
